      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Not all Scrabble dictionaries are created equal — at least not when it comes to bingos. SOWPODS (international) contains significantly more 7- and 8-letter words than TWL (North America), which directly impacts how often players can score the coveted 50-point bonus. Here's the data.</p>

