      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Bingo Probability Per Rack</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300">Given a random 7-tile draw from the standard bag, what's the probability that at least one valid bingo exists?</p>

